data.description: This meticulously maintained 3 bed, 2 bath home offers comfortable living across 1200 square feet. Step inside to discover an inviting open living area highlighted by a cozy gas fireplace and experience the ease of single level living with ample space. Centrally located in Norfolk within minutes of Virginia Zoo, Norfolk Botanical Garden, and Town Point Park. Come view this charming property TODAY!
